  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dc5\u0db8\u0dd4 \u0dc1\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dda\u0dab\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0d85\u0dba\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0db4\u0dad\u0dca \u0db7\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd3\u0db8 1 \u0dad\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The acceptance of applications for the first grade is extended until 1",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The date of calling for applications for the admission of students to the first grade of schools in the coming year 2023 has been extended to August 1.",
        "Due to the problematic situation in the country, the Ministry of Education said that this step was taken in consideration of the requests received from parents to extend the deadline for submitting applications for the enrollment of students in the first grade of 2023."
      ],
